The Healing Streams Live Healing Services has become phenomenal in manifesting a divine mandate bestowed on Pastor Chris Oyakhilome, President of Loveworld Incorporated, also known as Christ Embassy. The healing services take believers into a season of intercession, communion with the throne of God, and liberation of believers from earthly burdens. Pastor Chris leads an anointed and spirit-filled intermediary team of the Ministry to interface with the Throne of Grace and the congregation to the supernatural realm bringing down the down of God upon the oppressed, afflicted and the sick. 
The Healing Streams Live Healing Services have significantly yielded results, culminating to myriads of miracles and testimonies over the years. The 2022 session is no exception. 
Preceding the March 18 to 20 2022 edition of the largest Live Healing Crusade in world history is the 24-hour of prayer, miracles and testimonies themed Healing School Online Prayer Conference, which held in February. The event with billions across over 100 nations participating elicited global prayer chain. Participants were led to the realm of the supernatural floating as saints of God, praying in the Spirit, and making heartfelt intercession for the lost, the broken, the sick, infirmed, and all nations of the earth. Indeed it was monumental in the impartation of the touch of God, made possible by the presence and manifestation of the Holy Spirit.
