Specifically, the Healing School Online Prayer Conference commenced on Friday, February 4 at 6.00pm (GMT+1) with a session of worship, praise, and thanksgiving. Director of the Healing School, Pastor Deola Phillips, acquainted the participating global congregation, that prayer is “believers’ joyful response to the invitation of the Heavenly Father.” She, therefore, set the global congregation in motion, saying, “We will be praying in earnest fervency towards the Healing Streams Live Healing Services with Pastor Chris and we are so excited.”
Senior pastors and other invited guests in the Panel of Discussants, relayed their inspirations and strategies for the Healing Streams Live Healing Services, electrifying the global congregation with testimonies of miracles they received from participation in previous editions. Their discussions raised new hopes of divine visitation and encouragement amongst the congregation.  
Expressing gratitude to God for divine manifestation in her life, Sonia, 55years, from Italy, narrated shesuffered from anorexia and bulimia for 40 years and was filled with fear and anxiety. She received divine touch while attending the July 2021 Healing Streams Live Healing Services; saying that she was freed instantly when Pastor Chris laid hands on her. 
Her weight is now up, she is healthy and happy with her life.
Another testimony relayed that a little boy, Samuel Oladokun, was diagnosed with Wilm’s tumor, a cancer of the kidneys that left him in terrible pain and with a massively swollen abdomen. Samuel was healed by the power of God during the healing services.
These testimonies lifted spirit of the global online congregation, resulting in roll out of miracles from nations of the world during the prayers. Again, those who received divine touch, could not hold back their joy of the miracle.
