Norma writing from the Cayman Islands, highlighted: “I had been experiencing severe heart palpitations for more than three weeks. As Pastor Deola gave the word that the miracles had started, I received healing. The pain in my back disappeared and the palpitations ceased. Hallelujah!”
Also, Tina from Nicaragua testified: “As we were praying, Pastor Deola mentioned my mother’s case. For the past few years, my mother had been hearing noises in her head and in her ear but now she is completely fine.”
In preparation for the Healing Streams Live Healing Services in March, words of power proceeding from Man of God have set the stage for a glorious time, with clouds full of rain, and ready for outpouring to overflow the whole earth.With the assurance that “God answers when we pray, believers are advised to register for the Marchsession, being guided to visit www.healingstreams.tv/3daysfor registration as the manifesting divine mandate continues. 
 
